<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
    <title>Email de validation de compte</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .text-danger {
            color: #e55353 !important
        }

        .table-striped tbody tr:nth-of-type(odd) {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        h3 {
            orphans: 3;
            widows: 3;
        }

        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .text-left {
            text-align: left !important;
        }

        .text-uppercase {
            text-transform: uppercase !important;
        }

        button {
            border-radius: 0;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: inherit;
            line-height: inherit;
        }

        button:focus {
            outline: 5px auto -webkit-focus-ring-color;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 400;
            text-align: center;
            white-space: nowrap;
            vertical-align: middle;
            -webkit-user-select: none;
            -moz-user-select: none;
            -ms-user-select: none;
            user-select: none;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            transition: color 0.15s ease-in-out, background-color 0.15s ease-in-out, border-color 0.15s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.15s ease-in-out;
        }

        .btn:hover, .btn:focus {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn:focus, .btn.focus {
            outline: 0;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.25);
        }

        .btn-primary {
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #007bff;
            border-color: #007bff;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #0069d9;
            border-color: #0062cc;
        }

        .btn-primary:focus, .btn-primary.focus {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .text-center {
            text-align: center !important;
        }

        .small {
            font-size: 80%;
        }

        h2, .h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        h4, .h4 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .font-weight-bold {
            font-weight: 700 !important;
        }

        .mt-3 {
            margin-top: 1rem !important;
        }

        h3, .h3 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
        }

        h5, .h5 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<table class="table table-striped">
    <tr>
        <td style="height: 15px;"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="text-left text-uppercase">
            <h4 class="h4 font-weight-bold">Cher(e) {{ firstName }} {{ lastName }}</h4>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>
            <h5 class="h5">Bienvenu(e) sur l'application archivage de koh</h5>
            <p>Pour confirmer votre compte, veuillez suivre ce lien <a
                        href="{{ app.request.schemeAndHttpHost }}/confirmation-admin-account?compte_remember_token={{ random }}">confirmation
                    de compte</a> ou vous pouviez juste cliquer sur le button ci-dessous.</p>
            <a class="mt-3"
               href="{{ app.request.schemeAndHttpHost }}/confirmation-admin-account?compte_remember_token={{ random }}">
                <button class="btn btn-primary">cliquer ici pour confirmer</button>
            </a>
            <p class="text-danger mt-3">Si vous n'êtes pas l'auteur de cette demande pour la confirmation, veuillez
                ignorer
                ce mail.</p>
            <p class="text-center">Toute l'équipe vous souhaite la bienvenue.</p>
            <p class="small text-center text-uppercase"><a href="https://www.mbeyan.com">MBEYAN.COM</a> application
                archivage de koh
            </p>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
